# 🎓 SEL Academic Management App



> A Flutter-based mobile application for managing academic activities with role-based access across predefined semesters.

---

## 📝 Project Overview

The **SEL Academic Management App** is designed to streamline academic activities across **eight semesters**, providing a secure and organized digital platform for students, teachers, and administrators.

The system ensures **role-based access control**, so users can only access the sections and courses they are assigned to.

---

## 👥 User Roles & Permissions

### **Students**
- Registered using **student ID & mobile number**
- Can log in **only to their assigned semester**
- Can:
  - View enrolled courses 📚
  - Access course materials 📄
  - Track attendance ✅
  - See marks distribution 🏅
- **Read-only access** – cannot modify data

### **Teachers**
- Assigned to specific **courses & semesters**
- Can:
  - Upload & manage documents 📁
  - Create/update/delete course content ✏️
  - Record attendance 👨‍🏫
  - Enter/update marks 📝

### **Admin**
- Manages all predefined data:
  - Students
  - Teachers
  - Courses
  - Semesters
  - Assignments (Teacher-Course, Student-Semester)

---

## 🌟 Key Features

- 🔐 **Role-Based Access Control**
- 📱 **Flutter Cross-Platform Frontend**
- 🔑 **Firebase Authentication**
- 🗄️ **Supabase Database**
- 📂 **Document Management**
- ✅ **Attendance Tracking**
- 🏆 **Marks Management**
- 📊 **Organized Semester Management**

---

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

| Layer       | Technology                       |
|------------|----------------------------------|
| Frontend    | Flutter                          |
| Backend     | Firebase Authentication, Supabase |
| Database    | Supabase                         |
| Platform    | Android & iOS (Cross-platform)  |

